            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1emo%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1emo%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你每次emo都在伤胃#</span></a>😔】你知道吗？<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E5%92%8C%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%83%83%E7%96%BC%E5%92%8C%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#胃疼和情绪有关系#</span></a>。压抑性情绪，比如焦虑、抑郁、恐惧，常导致胃肠道动力低下；而亢奋的情绪，比如愤怒、生气，则会导致胃肠高动力反应，造成胃食管反流、胃炎。医生提醒：要保持心情舒畅，情绪不好时，可以通过运动来缓解。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （人民日报） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4939375637889118" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">人民日报的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0033ImPzly1hhbckhvu6zj60lw0cb0t702.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NaR7WXPUlx0888lfRjS801041200eQdY0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=788x444.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693257175&amp;ssig=eqOZlaFR0U&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/w669UZn0lx0888lhi8LS01041200aphJ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x362.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1693257175&amp;ssig=c%2BK2uXR3wE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A493937